        "created_at": "2025-06-05T12:49:55.046Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I would love to see a widget option that can send a pre-set message to a group. My specific use case is as a kind of a SOS button that would notify one of a group chat. Ideally this would also include my GPS coordinates. And a bonus would be if there was an option to repeat the message with updated coordinates on a set schedule until stopped.</p>",
