        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/avitus/{size}/34172_2.png",
        "created_at": "2025-06-06T14:38:16.634Z",
        "cooked": "<p>If youâ€™re broadcasting your location and that you need help, thereâ€™s no reason this needs to be a Signal function. There are plenty of options that already exist:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Life360</strong>: Has an SOS button that sends SMS alerts to designated emergency contacts when activated<a href=\"https://www.life360.com/learn/sos-alerts-with-emergency-dispatch\">1</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>SOS Alert by Solvaday</strong>: Activates a loud alarm, calls, and sends SMS with your location to emergency contacts. Can be triggered by shaking the phone or pressing the power button multiple times<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.solvaday.panic_alarm\">2</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>SOS Alert by Raghav Maheshwari</strong>: Sends your current location to emergency contacts via SMS, with customizable SOS messages and a one-touch widget<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.rghvsapp.android.sosalert\">3</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Red Panic Button</strong>: Sends SMS and email with GPS coordinates to emergency contacts with one button press<a href=\"https://www.redpanicbutton.com/\">4</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Send Help - SOS Panic Button (iOS)</strong>: Sends SMS, emails, and posts location on social media to pre-selected contacts with one tap<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/send-help-sos-panic-button/id517707164\">5</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Crises Control Panic Button App</strong>: Designed for employees, it sends GPS-tracked SOS alerts to emergency response teams with silent push notifications and real-time updates<a href=\"https://www.crises-control.com/products/sos-panic-button/\">6</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>SquareGlow Emergency SOS Button</strong>: A physical wireless SOS button that sends instant alerts and visual alarms to contacts via an app, working even without internet<a href=\"https://www.squareglow.com/products/squareglow-sos-button\">7</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Google Personal Safety (Pixel phones)</strong> and <strong>Noonlight by SafeTrek</strong>: Hold-to-activate SOS apps that alert emergency contacts unless canceled, with automatic location sharing<a href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/androidapps/comments/ugvtxa/app_that_alerts_an_emergency_contact_unless_you/\">8</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>",
